New: Test cases on complexity aperture metric module.
New: Test cases on PyPlanScoring kernel class and Complexity factor calculation
Fix: DVH calculation of rings, and broken adaptive rasterization of multiple contours per plane.
Fix: Fix halcyon SOP class UI - RT plan
Fix: Halcyon plans - SOP UID, Monaco plans using bastula-pydicom fork, new formatted xls repport on backend.

New: PyDVHItem operator overloading __add__ to merge absolute DVHs.

expression.expression-string: # Calculate a DVH from DICOM RT data struc_file = structure_files_dict[struc_name] dose_file = doses_files_dict[grad_name][dose_grid_name] calcdvh = dvhcalc.get_dvh(struc_file, dose_file, 2) dp_dose = calcdvh.cumulative.bincenters dp_vol = calcdvh.cumulative.counts plt.plot(dp_dose, dp_vol, label='dicompyler-core') # curve compare # grab analytical data sname = struc_adapter(struc_name) query = grad_adapter[grad_name] + ' ' + dose_grid_name + ' mm' an_dvh_df = analytical_curves[sname][query] an_dose_axis = analytical_curves[sname]['Dose (cGy)'] / 100.0 # get curve compare data cmp = CurveCompare(an_dose_axis, an_dvh_df, calc_data.dose_axis, calc_data.volume_cc) cmp.plot_results('Analytical', 'PyPlanScoring', struc_name[:-4] + ' - ' + query, results_folder)
